## About This Package

This package includes files copied from [Dockerhub Hub-tool](https://github.com/docker/hub-tool) at version `v0.4.5`.

### [Unreleased]

#### Added
- Copied `store.go` from https://github.com/docker/hub-tool/blob/main/pkg/credentials/store.go.
- Copied `main.go` from https://github.com/docker/hub-tool/blob/main/main.go

#### Modified
- Abstracted obtaining credentials from copied `main.go` into `GetCredentials` function
- Added more descriptive error messages when obtaining credentials fails

#### Fixed
- Added periods to end of sentences in comments
- Moved hardcoded values to constants
- Added directive `nolint:gosec` to ignore linting errors in `store.go`
